31\u20131933)}}\n|-\n| style=\"background:#fcc;\"| Opposition {{small|(1933)}}\n|-\n! [[1933 Spanish general election|1933]]\n| ''None''\n| {{Composition bar|59|473|hex={{Spanish Socialist Workers' Party/meta/color}}}}\n| [[File:Red Arrow Down.svg|10px]]57\n| [[Francisco Largo Caballero]]\n| style=\"background:#fcc;\"| Opposition\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"| [[1936 Spanish general election|1936]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Popular Front (Spain)|Popular Front]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"| {{Composition bar|99|473|hex={{Spanish Socialist Workers' Party/meta/color}}}}\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[File:Green Arrow Up Darker.svg|10px]]40\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Indalecio Prieto]]\n| style=\"background:#fcc;\"| Opposition {{small|(1936)}}\n|-\n| style=\"background:#cfc;\"| Government {{small|(1936\u20131939)}}\n|}\n\n===Cortes Generales===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:97%; text-align:left;\"\n|-\n| colspan=\"10\" align=\"center\"| [[Cortes Generales]]\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" width=\"75\"| Election\n! colspan=\"5\"| Congress\n! colspan=\"2\"| Senate\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Leading candidate\n! rowspan=\"2\"| {{abbr|Gov.|Government}}\n|-\n! width=\"70\"| Votes\n! width=\"35\"| %\n! width=\"25\"| #\n! Seats\n! width=\"35\"| +/\u2013\n! Seats\n! width=\"35\"| +/\u2013\n|-\n! [[1977 Spanish general election|1977]]\n| 5,371,866\n| 29.3\n| 2nd\n| {{Composition bar|118|350|hex={{Spanish Socialist Workers' Party/meta/color}}}}\n| \u2014\n| {{Composition bar|54|207|hex={{Spanish Socialist Workers' Party/meta/color}}}}\n| \u2014\n| rowspan=\"7\"| [[Felipe Gonz\u00e1lez]]\n| style=\"background:#fcc; text-align:center;\"| No\n|-\n! [[1979 Spanish general election|1979]]\n| 5,469,813\n| 30.4\n| 2nd\n| {{Composition bar|121|350|hex={{Spanish Socialist Workers' Party/meta/color}}}}\n| [[File:Green Arrow Up Darker.svg|10px]]3\n| {{Composition bar|69|208|hex={{Spanish Socialist Workers' Party/meta/color}}}}\n| [[File:Green Arrow Up Darker.svg|10px]]15\n| style=\"background:#fcc; text-align:center;\"| No\n|-\n! [[1982 Span