ied with https://starttls-everywhere.org/ or other}}\n! Tracking content prevention<ref name=EFF2019>{{cite web|url=https://www.eff.org/deeplinks/2019/01/stop-tracking-my-emails|title=(Don't) Return to Sender: How to Protect Yourself From Email Tracking|authors=Sydney Li and Bennett Cyphers|date=2019-01-09}}</ref>\n! Basic SPF{{efn|SPF is configured and outbound mail passes SPF test from default webmail and SMTP}}\n! SPF for custom domain and client{{efn|SPF can be configured on a custom domain with reserved IP address or shared addresses and anti-spoofing measures}}\n!Default DKIM{{efn|Outbound mail has a default DKIM signature by default}}\n!DKIM for custom domain and client{{efn|A custom DKIM signature can be generated for outbound mail and configured on a custom server}}\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" |Alice.it, [[Tin.it]]\n| ?\n| {{No}}<ref name=gtremailred/>\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[AOL Mail]]\n| {{No}}<ref name=gtremailred>{{cite web|url=https://transparencyreport.google.com/safer-email/overview?encrypt_region_table=encryption_level:RED;region:001&lu=encrypt_region_table|title=Google transparency report for safer email|accessdate=2020-04-12}}</ref>\n| ?\n| ?\n| ?\n| ?\n| ?\n| ?\n| ?\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Comcast]].net\n| ?\n| {{Yes}}<ref name=\"gtremailgreen\"/>\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[FastMail]]\n| ?\n| ?\n| ?\n| {{Yes}}\n| ?\n| ?\n| {{Yes}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fastmail.com/help/technical/senderauthentication.html#outbound|title=Sender authentication|website=Fastmail Help & Support|language=en|access-date=2020-04-12}}</ref>\n| ?\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Grupo Folha|Folha]] ([[bol.com.br]], [[uol.com.br]])\n| ?\n| {{No}}<ref name=\"gtremailred\"/>\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Gandi]]\n| ?\n| ?\n| ?\n| ?\n| ?\n| ?\n| {{No}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://docs.gandi.net/en/gandimail/faq/general_questions.html#does-gandimail-support-dkim|title=Frequent Questions: General Email Questions \u201